      'Potential suppliers',
      'Business procedures',
      'Fulfillment process',
      'Internet marketing',
      'Technical systems',
      'The internet',
      'E-marketing systems',
      'CRM systems',
      'Office automation',
      'How will you process your first order?',
    ],
    bizPlan: {
      label: 'Business plan piece',
      pieces: [
        'Technology',
        'IT processes',
      ],
    },
  },
  {
    num: '05',
    short: 'Management, Organization, HR & Strategy',
    title: 'Management, organization, HR and strategy',
    resolves: 'How the venture is led — formally, daily, and over the long arc.',
    body:
      'Phase five formalizes the operating discipline. Legal formation flows into governance; governance flows into strategic planning; strategic planning flows into the daily questions of communication, teamwork, hiring, location, and time. The course refuses the false choice between strategy and operations. Both are taught together because they are practiced together. The deliverable is the company&rsquo;s management and organization section, including the documented leadership method the founder will be measured against.',
    topics: [
      'Legal formation',
      'Strategic planning',
      'Written communication',
      'Verbal communication',
      'Teamwork',
      'Employee management',
      'Policies and practices',
      'Purchase an existing business',
      'Purchasing a franchise',
      'Taxation',
      'Location selection',
      'Leadership characteristics',
      'Leadership learning',
      'Leadership methods',
      'Time management',
    ],
    bizPlan: {
      label: 'Business plan piece',
      pieces: [
        'The company',
